	</A>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note18" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref18
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">18</A>
	<A HREF="
