	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,2,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Kock, <I>op. cit.</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">II</SPAN> p80.
	</A>
A verse precedes which may be translated: "My master, on receiving all his patrimony," and the point apparently is that the heir took what was a gift as his rightful due.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note19" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref19
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">19</A>
<I>Or.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">VII</SPAN>, wrongly attributed to Demosthenes. There is in § 5 a phrase similar to the one under comment.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note20" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref20
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">20</A>
Strictly, an inability to pronounce the letter "<SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">r</SPAN>," giving instead the sound of "<SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">l</SPAN>." See
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Alcibiades*.html#1.4
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
the <I>Alcibiades</I>, i.4</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note21" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref21
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">21</A>
A contemporary of Demosthenes.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note22" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref22
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">22</A>
357‑346 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note23" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref23
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">23</A>
<I>On the Crown</I>, § 18.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note24" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref24
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">24</A>
About 350 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> The speech "Against Meidias" (<I>Or.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">XXI</SPAN>) was never delivered. See § 154.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
