<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note29" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref29
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">29</A>
<I>Ors.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">IV</SPAN>, <SPAN CLASS="small">VI</SPAN>, <SPAN CLASS="small">IX</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note30" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref30
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">30</A>
Theopompus almost always displays hostility to Athens and her popular leaders.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
