<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note40" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Demosthenes*.html#ref40
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
